OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe court heard that Holden called the
OL,8,FNorth West Ambulance Service stating
OL,9,Fhe had 'attacked his wife' and that
OL,10,Fshe was 'heavily bleeding' from her
OL,11,Finjuries, on 5 July 2024. The medical
OL,12,Fservice contacted Cumbria Police after
OL,13,Fthe call.
OL,15,FFollowing the sentencing Suzanne
OL,16,FRedikin, Detective Inspector for
OL,17,FCumbria Police, said: "Holden made
OL,18,Fsignificant comments following his
OL,19,Farrest on the attack.
