OL,7,F"Holden knew the axe would cause
OL,8,Fpotentially fatal damage to the victim
OL,9,Fwhen he hit her three times.
OL,11,F"The use of any weapon has the
OL,12,Fpotential to end in tragedy, and the
OL,13,Fpolice and courts take such an act
OL,14,Fextremely seriously."
OL,16,FThe victim, who suffered a bleed on
OL,17,Fthe brain, was taken to the Royal
OL,18,FVictoria Infirmary - the attack left
OL,19,Fher struggling to speak.
