OL,7,FProsecutor Tim Evans told Carlisle
OL,8,FCrown Court a nearby neighbour heard
OL,9,Fshouting which stopped when there was
OL,10,Fa thump and the sound of something
OL,11,Fheavy hitting the floor.
OL,13,FHolden told the first police officer
OL,14,Fto arrive at the scene "she might drop
OL,15,Fdead at any second".
