OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe described in the aftermath how the
OL,8,Fweapon went "right through her skull",
OL,9,Falso telling police: "I actually meant
OL,10,Fto murder her"; "I think I made a big
OL,11,Fmistake"; and "I've been mentally
OL,12,Fquite unwell".
OL,14,FOn leaving the address, Holden told
OL,15,Fhis wife: "I'm going to jail. I'm so
OL,16,Fsorry. I love you."
OL,18,FThe woman described being attacked by
OL,19,Fher axe-wielding husband after he
OL,20,Fcalled her to a bedroom and sat her on
OL,21,Fa bed.
