OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FShe was taken initially to Carlisle's
OL,8,FCumberland Infirmary but then
OL,9,Ftransferred to the Royal Victoria
OL,10,FInfirmary in Newcastle due to the
OL,11,Fseverity of her injuries. She had
OL,12,Fsuffered a fractured skull and brain
OL,13,Fbruising, but had since made a
OL,14,Fsuccessful recovery and was intending
OL,15,Fto return to work.
OL,17,FHolden was described as being
OL,18,Fdelusional and paranoid during the
OL,19,Fmonths before his attack, and anxious
OL,20,Fabout undiagnosed health problems.
