OL,3,C'Knew the axe would potentially cause
OL,4,Cfatal damage' - Man jailed for wife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHis wife told police she was aware of
OL,8,Fhim previously drinking, taking drugs
OL,9,Fand not working. She told police she
OL,10,Fdidn't want to press charges or get
OL,11,Fhim into trouble, instead saying she
OL,12,Fwanted him to receive professional
OL,13,Fhelp.
OL,15,FHolden, initially charged with
OL,16,Fattempted murder, admitted the lesser
OL,17,Falternative offence of wounding with
OL,18,Fintent to cause grievous bodily harm.
