OL,7,FHe was sentenced at the crown court on
OL,8,FMonday, when Judge Nicholas Barker
OL,9,Frevealed Holden's wife had written him
OL,10,Fa letter, pleading for mercy.
OL,12,FJudge Barker also considered detailed
OL,13,Fbackground information including what
OL,14,Fhe said was a "helpful, thoughtful and
OL,15,Fbalanced" report from a psychiatrist
OL,16,Fwho had spoken of a challenging
OL,17,Fassessment of Holden.
