OL,7,F"I do accept, Daniel Holden, that you
OL,8,Fare deeply remorseful for your
OL,9,Factions," the judge told him as he
OL,10,Fpassed sentence.
OL,12,FBut Judge Barker said of the attack:
OL,13,F"Within your mental state there was a
OL,14,Fpremeditation to your actions. This
OL,15,Fwas not an off-the-cuff, spontaneous
OL,16,Fevent."
